vars: {
  d2-config: {
    layout-engine: elk
    theme-id: 4
  }
}
title: |md
  # Commit Index Advancement Algorithm
  Figure 8 Safety Rule Implementation
| {near: top-center}
direction: right
Start: "●" {
  shape: circle
  style.fill: "#4CAF50"
  width: 30
}
CheckLeader: "Is this node\nthe Leader?" {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#FFF9C4"
}
ReturnFalse: "Return false\n(no advancement)" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#FFCDD2"
}
GetLastLogIndex: "lastLogIndex =\nlen(log) - 1" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#E3F2FD"
}
LoopN: "FOR N = lastLogIndex\ndown to commitIndex + 1" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#E8F5E9"
}
CheckCurrentTerm: "log[N].term ==\ncurrentTerm?" {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#FFF9C4"
}
SkipEntry: "CONTINUE\n(skip previous-\nterm entries)" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#FFE0B2"
}
CountReplicas: "replicatedCount = 1\n(count self as leader)" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#E3F2FD"
}
LoopPeers: "FOR each peer i\nin matchIndex[]" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#E8F5E9"
}
CheckMatchIndex: "matchIndex[i] >= N?" {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#FFF9C4"
}
IncrementCount: "replicatedCount++" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#C8E6C9"
}
CheckMajority: "replicatedCount >=\nmajority?" {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#FFF9C4"
}
Commit: "commitIndex = N\npersist()\nsignal applyCond" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#4CAF50"
  style.font-color: white
  style.bold: true
}
ReturnTrue: "Return true\n(advanced)" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#C8E6C9"
}
NextN: "Next N\n(decrement)" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#F5F5F5"
}
ReturnFalseEnd: "Return false\n(no safe N found)" {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#FFCDD2"
}
# Connections
Start -> CheckLeader
CheckLeader -> ReturnFalse: "No" {
  style.stroke: "#F44336"
}
CheckLeader -> GetLastLogIndex: "Yes" {
  style.stroke: "#4CAF50"
}
GetLastLogIndex -> LoopN
LoopN -> CheckCurrentTerm
CheckCurrentTerm -> SkipEntry: "No\n(Figure 8\nviolation)" {
  style.stroke: "#FF9800"
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
CheckCurrentTerm -> CountReplicas: "Yes" {
  style.stroke: "#4CAF50"
}
SkipEntry -> NextN
CountReplicas -> LoopPeers
LoopPeers -> CheckMatchIndex
CheckMatchIndex -> IncrementCount: "Yes" {
  style.stroke: "#4CAF50"
}
CheckMatchIndex -> LoopPeers: "No" {
  style.stroke: "#9E9E9E"
  style.stroke-dash: 2
}
IncrementCount -> LoopPeers {
  style.stroke: "#4CAF50"
}
LoopPeers -> CheckMajority: "loop\ndone"
CheckMajority -> Commit: "Yes\n(quorum)" {
  style.stroke: "#4CAF50"
  style.bold: true
}
CheckMajority -> NextN: "No" {
  style.stroke: "#F44336"
}
Commit -> ReturnTrue
NextN -> CheckCurrentTerm: "N > commitIndex" {
  style.stroke: "#2196F3"
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
NextN -> ReturnFalseEnd: "N <= commitIndex" {
  style.stroke: "#9E9E9E"
}
# Annotations
Legend: {
  near: bottom-right
  style.fill: "#FAFAFA"
  style.stroke: "#E0E0E0"
  CurrentTerm: "Current-term entry\n(safe to commit)" {
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#C8E6C9"
  }
  PreviousTerm: "Previous-term entry\n(skip - Figure 8)" {
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#FFE0B2"
  }
  Success: "Commit success" {
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#4CAF50"
    style.font-color: white
  }
  Fail: "No advancement" {
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#FFCDD2"
  }
}
Formula: |md
  **Majority Calculation:**
  
  majority = floor(N / 2) + 1
  where N = total nodes in cluster
  For 5-node cluster: majority = 3
  
| {near: bottom-left}
Figure8Note: |md
  **Figure 8 Safety Rule:**
  Only commit entries from the **current term**.
  Previous-term entries are committed *transitively* when a current-term entry commits after them.
  This prevents the scenario where:
  - Entry at index N (term T-1) replicated to majority
  - New leader elected (term T) with different entry at N
  - Would overwrite "committed" entry → **SAFETY VIOLATION**
| {near: bottom-center}